body:
I vote for FREEDOM
I vote for life
I vote for religious freedom
I vote for the unborn
I vote for medical freedom
I vote for the end of human trafficking
I vote for a multitude of other reasons
...I vote Donald J. Trump
.
.
and I did It all with my girls watching + taking notes on how to make our voices heard
.
.
Addie was 10 days old, last election. Today, four years later, she was filled with questions as we walked over to the neighborhood school + waited in line, to exercise our right!
.
.
I pray for the leaders of our nation, regardless of who wins, and I promise I’ll still be your friend + family, regardless of who you voted for!
.
.
One love, y’all!
author: shea.collective

body: Remember, people deserve love and kindness. And it’s on us to be decent to the people we are around. Share love. Share beauty. Be kind. I didn’t write this and I wish I knew who did, but I had a lot of people say they loved it on my stories yesterday so here it is to easily share! ✨🖤🦋
